 b e n e f i t s                        
                                        
 braille art provides several advantages
for blind and visually impaired users:  
                                        
#a.  enhanced  understanding:  visual   
concepts become tactile                 
#b.  educational  value:  diagrams,     
charts, and illustrations in  braille   
#c.  complete  accessibility:  no       
information is lost in conversion       
#d.  professional  quality:  suitable   
for embosser printing                   
                                        
 the  pratibimb converter automatically:
-  processes image references in text   
-  converts images to optimal  braille  
patterns                                
-  maintains proper formatting for      
embossers                               
-  includes descriptive text and titles 
-  ensures tactile clarity and          
readability                             
                                        
